==Abstract==

This IIP specifies HTLC (Hash Time-Locked Contract) operations within Lightning channels, adapted from BOLT #2 for ML-DSA-87 signatures.

==Specification==

===Adding HTLCs===

To add an HTLC, send '''update_add_htlc''':

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! Description
|-
| channel_id || Channel identifier
|-
| id || HTLC ID (incrementing per channel)
|-
| amount_mint || Payment amount
|-
| payment_hash || SHA3-256 hash of preimage
|-
| cltv_expiry || Absolute timeout block height
|-
| onion_routing_packet || Encrypted routing data
|}

===Fulfilling HTLCs===

To fulfill an HTLC, send '''update_fulfill_htlc''':

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! Description
|-
| channel_id || Channel identifier
|-
| id || HTLC ID being fulfilled
|-
| payment_preimage || 32-byte preimage
|}

===Failing HTLCs===

To fail an HTLC, send '''update_fail_htlc''':

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! Description
|-
| channel_id || Channel identifier
|-
| id || HTLC ID being failed
|-
| reason || Encrypted failure reason
|}

===Commitment Signing===

After HTLC updates, exchange '''commitment_signed''':

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! Description
|-
| channel_id || Channel identifier
|-
| signature || Commitment tx signature (4627 bytes)
|-
| htlc_signatures || Signatures for HTLC outputs
|}

===Revocation===

After receiving commitment signature, send '''revoke_and_ack''':

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Field !! Description
|-
| channel_id || Channel identifier
|-
| per_commitment_secret || Secret for previous commitment
|-
| next_per_commitment_point || Point for next commitment
|}

===HTLC States===

<pre>
LOCAL_PROPOSED → LOCAL_COMMITTED → LOCAL_IRREVOCABLY_COMMITTED
REMOTE_PROPOSED → REMOTE_COMMITTED → REMOTE_IRREVOCABLY_COMMITTED
                → FULFILLED | FAILED | REMOVED
</pre>

